          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Known amounts of powdered Y/2-O/3 were homogeneously",
                "distributed on iron foils (thickness 8.2-mum) and",
                "coated by silicon resin.  By folding up sandwiches,",
                "area 25-mm**2, were made.  Twelve of these iron-yttrium",
                "oxide- iron sandwiches were pilled up on an aluminium",
                "backing also by means of the silicon adhesive.  The",
                "thickness of the resin layers were unimportant for the",
                "further procedure.  The mean thickness of an yttrium",
                "oxide layer amount to about 1-mum."
              ]
            }
          ],
